name: Bunnie
description: Bunnie is a meme token on the Solana Blockchain, specifically focussed on outlining the adventures of Bunnie who is a character and one of many that live in the BunVerse. this project will establish the BunVerse and will introduce new characters and new tokens which can be listed in the future. Of particular importance is the introduction of original art which is differentiated from other memes which use AI generation
